    <title>LocationManager解析(基于10.0)</title>
    <url>/2020/07/11/LocationManager%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-应用"><a href="#1-应用" class="headerlink" title="1. 应用"></a>1. 应用</h2><p>LocationManager应用例子，locationManager.getBestProvider获取最好的定位方式，locationManager.requestLocationUpdates是开始获取定位。需要获取定位，有设备GPS方式，另外一种是NLP方式，就是NETWORK_PROVIDER，NETWORK_PROVIDER由第三方提供，由系统集成NLP模块获取定位。</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Criteria criteria = <span class="keyword">new</span> Criteria();</span><br><span class="line">criteria.setAccuracy(Criteria.ACCURACY_COARSE);<span class="comment">//低精度，如果设置为高精度，依然获取不了location。</span></span><br><span class="line">criteria.setAltitudeRequired(<span class="keyword">false</span>);<span class="comment">//不要求海拔</span></span><br><span class="line">criteria.setBearingRequired(<span class="keyword">false</span>);<span class="comment">//不要求方位</span></span><br><span class="line">criteria.setCostAllowed(<span class="keyword">true</span>);<span class="comment">//允许有花费</span></span><br><span class="line">criteria.setPowerRequirement(Criteria.POWER_LOW);<span class="comment">//低功耗</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//获取LocationManager</span></span><br><span class="line">LocationManager locationManager = (LocationManager) getSystemService(Context.LOCATION_SERVICE);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 获取最好的定位方式</span></span><br><span class="line">String provider = locationManager.getBestProvider(criteria, <span class="keyword">true</span>); <span class="comment">// true 代表从打开的设备中查找</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 获取所有可用的位置提供器</span></span><br><span class="line">List&lt;String&gt; providerList = locationManager.getProviders(<span class="keyword">true</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 测试一般都在室内，这里颠倒了书上的判断顺序</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (providerList.contains(LocationManager.NETWORK_PROVIDER)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    provider = LocationManager.NETWORK_PROVIDER;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (providerList.contains(LocationManager.GPS_PROVIDER)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    provider = LocationManager.GPS_PROVIDER;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 当没有可用的位置提供器时，弹出Toast提示用户</span></span><br><span class="line">    Toast.makeText(<span class="keyword">this</span>, <span class="string">"Please Open Your GPS or Location Service"</span>, Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Log.d(<span class="string">"provider"</span>, <span class="string">" provider = "</span> + provider);</span><br><span class="line">LocationListener locationListener = <span class="keyword">new</span> LocationListener() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//当位置改变的时候调用</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onLocationChanged</span><span class="params">(Location location)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//经度</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">double</span> longitude = location.getLongitude();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//纬度</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">double</span> latitude = location.getLatitude();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//海拔</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">double</span> altitude = location.getAltitude();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        locationStr = longitude + <span class="string">"_"</span> + latitude;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//当GPS状态发生改变的时候调用</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onStatusChanged</span><span class="params">(String provider, <span class="keyword">int</span> status, Bundle extras)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">switch</span> (status) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">case</span> LocationProvider.AVAILABLE:</span><br><span class="line">                message = <span class="string">"当前GPS为可用状态!"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                Log.d(<span class="string">"provider"</span>, <span class="string">" message = "</span> + message);</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">case</span> LocationProvider.OUT_OF_SERVICE:</span><br><span class="line">                message = <span class="string">"当前GPS不在服务内!"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                Log.d(<span class="string">"provider"</span>, <span class="string">" message = "</span> + message);</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">case</span> LocationProvider.TEMPORARILY_UNAVAILABLE:</span><br><span class="line">                message = <span class="string">"当前GPS为暂停服务状态!"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                Log.d(<span class="string">"provider"</span>, <span class="string">" message = "</span> + message);</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//GPS开启的时候调用</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onProviderEnabled</span><span class="params">(String provider)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        message = <span class="string">"GPS开启了!"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        Log.d(<span class="string">"provider"</span>, <span class="string">" message = "</span> + message);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//GPS关闭的时候调用</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onProviderDisabled</span><span class="params">(String provider)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        message = <span class="string">"GPS关闭了!"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        Log.d(<span class="string">"provider"</span>, <span class="string">" message = "</span> + message);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//获取上次的location</span></span><br><span class="line">Location location = locationManager.getLastKnownLocation(provider);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * 参1:选择定位的方式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * 参2:定位的间隔时间</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * 参3:当位置改变多少时进行重新定位</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * 参4:位置的回调监听</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> */</span></span><br><span class="line">locationManager.requestLocationUpdates(provider, <span class="number">10000</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, locationListener);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="2-LocationManagerService启动"><a href="#2-LocationManagerService启动" class="headerlink" title="2. LocationManagerService启动"></a>2. LocationManagerService启动</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">systemRunning</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ...    </span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">// prepare providers：系统一启动，就开始准备Provider</span></span><br><span class="line">	initializeProvidersLocked();</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">initializeProvidersLocked</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 生成GPS_PROVIDER对象</span></span><br><span class="line">	LocationProvider gnssProviderManager = <span class="keyword">new</span> LocationProvider(GPS_PROVIDER, <span class="keyword">true</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// mRealProviders数据保存该值</span></span><br><span class="line">    mRealProviders.add(gnssProviderManager);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 添加至mProviders列表中</span></span><br><span class="line">    addProviderLocked(gnssProviderManager);</span><br><span class="line">	GnssLocationProvider gnssProvider = <span class="keyword">new</span> GnssLocationProvider(mContext,</span><br><span class="line">		gnssProviderManager,</span><br><span class="line">		mHandler.getLooper());</span><br><span class="line">	gnssProviderManager.attachLocked(gnssProvider);  </span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// bind to network provider：NETWORK_PROVIDER默认，是为空，需要第三方修改再提供APK，然后系统再修改，指定相应的包名，功能Feature为NLP</span></span><br><span class="line">    LocationProvider networkProviderManager = <span class="keyword">new</span> LocationProvider(NETWORK_PROVIDER, <span class="keyword">true</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    LocationProviderProxy networkProvider = LocationProviderProxy.createAndBind(</span><br><span class="line">            mContext,</span><br><span class="line">            networkProviderManager,</span><br><span class="line">            NETWORK_LOCATION_SERVICE_ACTION,</span><br><span class="line">            com.android.internal.R.bool.config_enableNetworkLocationOverlay,</span><br><span class="line">            com.android.internal.R.string.config_networkLocationProviderPackageName,</span><br><span class="line">            com.android.internal.R.array.config_locationProviderPackageNames);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (networkProvider != <span class="keyword">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        mRealProviders.add(networkProviderManager);</span><br><span class="line">        addProviderLocked(networkProviderManager);</span><br><span class="line">        networkProviderManager.attachLocked(networkProvider);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Slog.w(TAG, <span class="string">"no network location provider found"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="comment">// bind to geocoder provider：经纬度解析为位置文本 Provider</span></span><br><span class="line">    mGeocodeProvider = GeocoderProxy.createAndBind(mContext,</span><br><span class="line">		com.android.internal.R.bool.config_enableGeocoderOverlay,</span><br><span class="line">		com.android.internal.R.string.config_geocoderProviderPackageName,</span><br><span class="line">		com.android.internal.R.array.config_locationProviderPackageNames);</span><br><span class="line">    ...  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="3-使用流程"><a href="#3-使用流程" class="headerlink" title="3.使用流程"></a>3.使用流程</h2><p>基于上面应用的例子，LocationManager.getProviders(true);通过LocationManager，用Binder再调用至LocationManagerService，查找LocationManagerService中的方法，重点流程方法： getBestProvider， getProviders， requestLocationUpdates</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> String <span class="title">getBestProvider</span><span class="params">(Criteria criteria, <span class="keyword">boolean</span> enabledOnly)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//criteria：获取要求</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//enabledOnly:获取当前Provider中，可用或者不可用。Provider可以添加，但未启用</span></span><br><span class="line">    List&lt;String&gt; providers = getProviders(criteria, enabledOnly);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (providers.isEmpty()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        providers = getProviders(<span class="keyword">null</span>, enabledOnly);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (!providers.isEmpty()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (providers.contains(GPS_PROVIDER)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> GPS_PROVIDER;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (providers.contains(NETWORK_PROVIDER)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> NETWORK_PROVIDER;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> providers.get(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> List&lt;String&gt; <span class="title">getProviders</span><span class="params">(Criteria criteria, <span class="keyword">boolean</span> enabledOnly)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 判断权限</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">int</span> allowedResolutionLevel = getCallerAllowedResolutionLevel();</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">synchronized</span> (mLock) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// mProviders在 “2启动” addProviderLocked(gnssProviderManager);方法中</span></span><br><span class="line">		ArrayList&lt;String&gt; providers = <span class="keyword">new</span> ArrayList&lt;&gt;(mProviders.size());</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">for</span> (LocationProvider provider : mProviders) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">			String name = provider.getName();</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (FUSED_PROVIDER.equals(name)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			&#125;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (allowedResolutionLevel &lt; getMinimumResolutionLevelForProviderUseLocked(name)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 权限与级别</span></span><br><span class="line">				<span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			&#125;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (enabledOnly &amp;&amp; !provider.isUseableLocked()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 判断获取的是需要可用，还是不可用的</span></span><br><span class="line">				<span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			&#125;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span> (criteria != <span class="keyword">null</span></span><br><span class="line">					&amp;&amp; !android.location.LocationProvider.propertiesMeetCriteria(</span><br><span class="line">					name, provider.getPropertiesLocked(), criteria)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			&#125;</span><br><span class="line">			providers.add(name);</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">return</span> providers;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>最后使用方法：requestLocationUpdates，来最终获取地理位置信息</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">requestLocationUpdates</span><span class="params">(LocationRequest request, ILocationListener listener,</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="params">        PendingIntent intent, String packageName)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ... <span class="comment">//代码判断权限</span></span><br><span class="line">    requestLocationUpdatesLocked(sanitizedRequest, receiver, uid, packageName);</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">requestLocationUpdatesLocked</span><span class="params">(LocationRequest request, Receiver receiver,</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="params">		<span class="keyword">int</span> uid, String packageName)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">    applyRequirementsLocked(name);	</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">applyRequirementsLocked</span><span class="params">(LocationProvider provider)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 核心方法，调用使用Provider的方法setRequestLocked，调用setRequest，请求地理位置</span></span><br><span class="line">    provider.setRequestLocked(providerRequest, worksource</span><br><span class="line">    ...</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>调用请求setRequest后，Provider获取数据完成后，会调用LocationProviderBase的reportLocation方法，再调用ILocationProviderManager的onReportLocation回调数据。后续再通过ILocationListener回调至请求app，完成一次请求地理位置数据流程。</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">onReportLocation</span><span class="params">(Location location)</span> </span>&#123;    </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
